      </p>
      <p>To install Power Base Library and Power Contract Lifecycle Management, see <xref href="https://documentation.Power.com/clm/february-23/installing-Power-clm-203494216.html"
               format="html"
               scope="external">
            <u>Installing Power CLM</u>
         </xref>.</p>
      <note type="note">
